T*
(it is linked to examples, revision drills, and exam-style questions that reflect how) Tj
T*
(Mathematics is assessed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Examples) Tj
T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on finding the derivative of a polynomial and using it as) Tj
T*
(slope.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in derivative rules and interpreting gradient that the) Tj
T*
(question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Differentiation step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Example 2) Tj
T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on power rule and tangent-gradient) Tj
T*
(questions.) Tj
T*
(2. Break the task into smaller parts and link each part to the rule being used.) Tj
T*
(3. Point out how to avoid forgetting to reduce the power correctly or mishandling) Tj
T*
(constants while solving it.) Tj
T*
(4. Review the result and connect it back to the topic overview.) Tj
